modules.description: This module provides the `run` function to initialize and manage a random number generator using entropy from a CPU RNG and `getrandom()`, integrated with Eio's environment. It works with `Mirage_crypto_rng.generator` and `Mirage_crypto_rng_eio.env` types, handling entropy collection and periodic reseeding. A concrete use case is setting up a secure RNG context within an Eio-based application to ensure cryptographic operations have sufficient entropy.
